metadata.name: hide&seak
metadata.description:
The photo "Hide&Seak" captures the peaceful serenity of a tranquil lake. Some small wooden boats sitting idly, as if waiting for someone to come and take one out on the water. The lake itself is a shimmering expanse of crystal-clear water, reflecting the bright blue sky above. The sun casts a warm glow across the scene. The photo is a reminder of the simple pleasures that can be found in the great outdoors, and the joy of exploring the world around us. 

This is my first nft, so you, the collector may expect some future benefits.
